{"tid":33116,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[Kodi]開源多媒體影音中心 + 廣東話片源教學","createTime":"2016-12-10T15:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T19:31:49.000Z","uid":12599,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"773f1f5cd0d73c52254d3069217beb11f9f35f49","tid":33116,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"Kodi出左都好長時間下,佢係一個整合左的multimedia center software,可以俾用家好輕易咁搵到想睇的片源<br />\n<br />\n片源可以係local (HDD/SSD), NAS, server,或者其他人開發的addon<br />\n當中有正版片源,亦有非正式版權片源,但Kodi本身係開源,唔涉及版權問題<br />\n<br />\n廣東話片源大部份都係非合法source,以下只係交流用途一切後果自負<br />\n<br />\nkodi係跨平台software,win mac linux ios android raspberry都有,可以係呢度下載:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kodi.tv/download/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkodi.tv%2Fdownload%2F&d=8u2at2%2F5jYIHtQWMt3fKIwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=6d355fbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://kodi.tv/download/</a><br />\n<br />\n跟住係片源,setting大致跟呢條video:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlfN3p1Ob8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJlfN3p1Ob8s&d=8u2at2%2F5jYIHtQWMt3fKIwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=4beaba56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlfN3p1Ob8s</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東話片源主要係用AZdrama同ICdrama,日韓台中港片都有,唔似小米果d咁要VPN就可以直接睇,片入面無俾link,但係google 打azdrama zip download就可以了,建議經repository安裝zip,更新會方便d<br />\n<br />\n聽電台就有Hong Kong Radio<br />\n<br />\n睇西片/劇就用Exodus<br />\n<a href=\"https://seo-michael.co.uk/how-to-install-exodus-for-kodi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fseo-michael.co.uk%2Fhow-to-install-exodus-for-kodi%2F&d=8u2at2%2F5jYIHtQWMt3fKIwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=7d367b06\" target=\"_blank\">https://seo-michael.co.uk/how-to-install-exodus-for-kodi/</a><br />\n<br />\n字幕我用shooter完全搵唔到野,<a href=\"http://建議用opensubtitle.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E7%94%A8opensubtitle.org&d=8u2at2%2F5jYIHtQWMt3fKIwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=507f908c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">建議用opensubtitle.org</a>,不過得英文字幕,夠唔夠用就睇人啦<br />\n<br />\n想睇波就可以申請ustvnow,同埋係kodi入面裝佢個addon,登入後有45日試睇高清:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ustvnow.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ustvnow.com%2F&d=8u2at2%2F5jYIHtQWMt3fKIwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=a73994f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ustvnow.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你有隻舊的小米俾人block左VPN,可以試下裝kodi,暫時都幾多野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05e14a63427e2e4d5121e9734eafe891b7c81bc","tid":33116,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"如果想經repository安裝azdrama,可以跟呢個教學:<br />\n<br />\n1. File Manager<br />\n2. Add Source<br />\n3. Click &lt;None&gt;<br />\n3. 打 <a href=\"https://cthlo.github.io/cthlo-kodi-repo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcthlo.github.io%2Fcthlo-kodi-repo%2F&d=8u2at2%2F5jYIHtQWMt3fKIwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=73039455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cthlo.github.io/cthlo-kodi-repo/</a><br />\n4. Done, Name果度打 cthlo-kodi-repo<br />\n5. 返回home screen<br />\n6. 去system-&gt;addon-&gt;install from zip (唔係repository)<br />\n7. 安裝左 url resolver先<br />\n8. 安裝 addon installer<br />\n9. 安裝 AZdrama同ICdrama,搞掂<br />\n10. Hong Kong Radio可以係addon installer的music 搵度<br />\n11. 如果你聽開podcast網台,都可以加入kodi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33d2315b7ea568755ea6de6de71b3649b7c1de5","tid":33116,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s30.postimg.org/6ym0zlm1t/Untitled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs30.postimg.org%2F6ym0zlm1t%2FUntitled.jpg&h=f8cadc5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成功後大概係咁樣,大家都可以叫kodi連返上NAS睇片架,個UI好流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dede53051359cc70de5370caf061965938fe2fa3","tid":33116,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"另外kodi一樣有趣的地方就係有手機remote,即係好似chromecast airplay咁係同一個wifi network可以控制部電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果用remote的話推薦用第三方app(因為係opensource) Yatse,會比官方的Ko re更多功能,UI更靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nYatse可以係app store下載"},{"pid":"9229e4591c2187f109c101263da639012822923e","tid":33116,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"518441c4602226b66c45141e1bea0405e63ecda5","tid":33116,"uid":37063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:14:47.000Z","msg":"一直用樂視個盒睇KODI<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd6dc40f04b4e7c1de80ab1427f3e6bdc963beb","tid":33116,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T22:15:15.000Z","msg":"OSMC用家留明"},{"pid":"329ac78f966331870f5a589089b2323d330510fe","tid":33116,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:43:54.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4641c144c1e47a95a110944131e7c53182eebb25","tid":33116,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:31:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ffdff263ac220468dbb23602a9eba22d85d68511","tid":33116,"uid":65745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:38:17.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"11137d6d881f13daf5f157c3843ecf68a386e74b","tid":33116,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2